## AI / Human Collaboration

**AI does**: Code generation following established patterns, test implementation, docstrings, refactoring within architectural boundaries.

**Human does**: Architectural decisions beyond existing patterns, code review, security-sensitive implementations, production deployment.

**Escalate to human when**: Requirements are ambiguous, a decision is outside existing SAO.md patterns, or code touches auth/security/secrets.

**Quality gates (in order):**
1. All tests pass (`make test`)
2. Coverage ≥ 80% (`make test`)
3. Lint + types pass (`make check`)
4. Docstrings on all public APIs
5. Human review before merge

